KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.util module

KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.util.cos_sim(a: Tensor, b: Tensor)

Computes the cosine similarity cos_sim(a[i], b[j]) for all i and j. :return: Matrix with res[i][j] = cos_sim(a[i], b[j])

KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.util.dot_score(a: Tensor, b: Tensor)

Computes the dot-product dot_prod(a[i], b[j]) for all i and j. :return: Matrix with res[i][j] = dot_prod(a[i], b[j])

KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.util.download_and_unzip(url: str, out_dir: str, chunk_size: int = 1024) → str
KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.util.download_url(url: str, save_path: str, chunk_size: int = 1024)

Download url with progress bar using tqdm https://stackoverflow.com/questions/15644964/python-progress-bar-and-downloads

Args:

url (str): downloadable url save_path (str): local path to save the downloaded file chunk_size (int, optional): chunking of files. Defaults to 1024.
